{"tid":1899252,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"DIY 氣密蓋/口罩蓋教學 人人都做到","createTime":"2020-02-26T13:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T06:47:21.000Z","uid":335862,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b729c1cf4a978a4d4edca7eb778aab40c3e9137","tid":1899252,"uid":335862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"新手第一次開post，多多指教<br />\n可以直接睇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅字口罩蓋步驟</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃字氣密蓋步驟</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟見大家都搵緊氣密蓋/口罩蓋希望可以省一邊棉/罐。我都覺得對2097用一次就要棄好浪費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係我要棄對棉既時候突然有個諗法。就係自己DIY 氣密蓋/口罩蓋。<br />\n我知有好多手足用3D print 整左d蓋用。不過3D print 要既時間一啲都唔短又唔係人人都搵到3Dprinter 所以希望呢個方法幫到大家，成本50蚊左右，唔計對棉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">口罩蓋材料：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 用完既2097（p100）（要消毒）<br />\n2. 闊嘴水樽連蓋<br />\n3. 3秒ok 膠/AA膠<br />\n4. 熱熔膠（無就去五金買支AB膠，紅色包裝係快乾，藍色係慢乾)<br />\n5. 水磨砂紙（建議400度）<br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n1. 係對2097到Cut 扣具出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdNDqHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdNDqHa.png&h=af247b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 如果整口罩蓋就沿樽頸Cut 個樽頭出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21ynSnq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21ynSnq.png&h=a54df85d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 用砂紙磨齊cut 出嚟個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TsgcnL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TsgcnL.png&h=51d08360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 用AA膠（ok膠）黐實佢！等佢乾！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7p3yY20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7p3yY20.png&h=7a1fb01f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 用熱熔膠（AB膠）將接合個位封多一次，以免漏氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6mD99V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6mD99V.png&h=554cb500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. 燒熱一啲圓柱體既金屬係個樽蓋到開一啲窿仔。<br />\n7. 之後將一個口罩開六份，然之後扭上去就用得。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAFhGg4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAFhGg4.png&h=4ff26e85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aCMQgQx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaCMQgQx.png&h=07ed5b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">氣密蓋材料：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 用完既2097（p100）（要消毒）<br />\n2. 闊嘴水樽蓋<br />\n3. 3秒ok 膠/AA膠<br />\n4. 熱熔膠（無就去五金買支AB膠，紅色包裝係快乾，藍色係慢乾)<br />\n5. 水磨砂紙（建議400度）<br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n1. 係對2097到Cut 扣具出黎<br />\n2. 用砂紙磨齊樽蓋底啲鋸齒<br />\n3. 用AA膠（ok膠）黐實佢！等佢乾！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhKZaaW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhKZaaW.png&h=cf2b4280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 用熱熔膠（AB膠）將接合個位封多一次，以免漏氣。完成</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nrMzCP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nrMzCP.png&h=e8b33351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望人人都可以行多一步做多少少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果大家有咩建議大家討論。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1384cf2adea3cee491c268611af578b55111a30b","tid":1899252,"uid":335862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944c82602ecc6d02072924e0d161464c3ca0356f","tid":1899252,"uid":173538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d26e80c35bfceb341e2c53801a9e149f75be43","tid":1899252,"uid":108006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"呢個口罩蓋正，方便更換，好過用橡根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}